The daytime view is not

573
00:37:13,920 --> 00:37:15,680
as beautiful as the night now.

574
00:37:16,880 --> 00:37:17,760
Besides,

575
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:20,440
there are coworkers here in the daytime.

576
00:37:20,560 --> 00:37:21,720
What's wrong with coworkers?

577
00:37:22,120 --> 00:37:23,720
Just introduce me to them.

578
00:37:25,440 --> 00:37:27,000
If I were 20 years old,

579
00:37:27,640 --> 00:37:29,840
I'd introduce you to everyone.

580
00:37:31,360 --> 00:37:33,200
But I'm almost 40 years old now.

581
00:37:34,560 --> 00:37:36,320
I don't want people

582
00:37:36,360 --> 00:37:37,840
to gossip behind my back.

583
00:37:38,680 --> 00:37:39,840
Why don't you get married?

584
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,040
I don't want kids.

585
00:37:46,200 --> 00:37:48,240
I can't find a reason
to get married, either.

586
00:37:48,480 --> 00:37:50,200
Being unfettered like what I am now.

587
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,080
Isn't it nice?

588
00:37:54,880 --> 00:37:56,960
Maybe that's why you don't want
to go home.

589
00:37:57,880 --> 00:37:59,040
It's too lonely there.

590
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:03,680
Why don't you ever take me home?

591
00:38:05,920 --> 00:38:07,400
My home is too small,

592
00:38:07,480 --> 00:38:08,320
too messy.

593
00:38:09,160 --> 00:38:10,400
Building Ten in Yuling.

594
00:38:10,880 --> 00:38:11,840
A luxury mansion, right?

595
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,600
Rented.

596
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:17,400
I'm afraid

597
00:38:19,040 --> 00:38:20,360
we'll never get a result.

598
00:38:21,560 --> 00:38:22,640
Marriage is the only result?

599
00:38:23,640 --> 00:38:24,600
I don't think so.

600
00:38:25,160 --> 00:38:26,400
Just enjoy the moment.

601
00:38:31,240 --> 00:38:32,360
I have to go on a business trip.

602
00:38:32,920 --> 00:38:33,720
How long?

603
00:38:35,400 --> 00:38:36,400
Maybe a week.

604
00:38:39,080 --> 00:38:40,160
Will you miss me?

605
00:38:41,400 --> 00:38:42,920
I miss you already.

606
00:38:44,120 --> 00:38:45,080
Really?

607
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:03,320
Dad,

608
00:39:05,160 --> 00:39:06,640
their boss is out of town today.

609
00:39:06,640 --> 00:39:07,600
He asked me to greet you.

610
00:39:08,160 --> 00:39:08,920
No need to be polite.

611
00:39:09,080 --> 00:39:10,880
I'm counting on them to make me money.

612
00:39:14,220 --> 00:39:16,100
[Su Qian]

613
00:39:16,800 --> 00:39:18,480
This is
the Canadian cancer screening equipment

614
00:39:18,640 --> 00:39:20,320
I told you about before.

615
00:39:21,160 --> 00:39:22,640
It's the only company in China

616
00:39:22,680 --> 00:39:24,360
[WYLON]
that has this technology.

617
00:39:24,880 --> 00:39:26,120
This project proposal

618
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:27,800
has no Chinese version?

619
00:39:28,160 --> 00:39:28,800
Yes, there is.

620
00:39:29,400 --> 00:39:30,800
I'll translate it and bring it to you.

621
00:39:30,800 --> 00:39:32,040
I'm Susan's friend.

622
00:39:32,360 --> 00:39:33,320
She's on a business trip.

623
00:39:34,560 --> 00:39:35,640
She told me.

624
00:39:35,720 --> 00:39:36,840
She's already arranged it for me.

625
00:39:37,680 --> 00:39:39,560
This is Mr. Chen from Nanlin Mining.

626
00:39:39,640 --> 00:39:40,880
He wants to know more about our company.

627
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:43,680
Fei Ke waltzed into Wylon
with Su Qian's staff ID

628
00:39:43,880 --> 00:39:45,640
and took a tour.

629
00:39:45,680 --> 00:39:46,880
Mr. Chen was convinced

630
00:39:47,800 --> 00:39:49,400
and handed over the money to him.

631
00:39:49,400 --> 00:39:50,120
Bye.

632
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:52,640
However, at the time,
Su Qian was out on a business trip.

633
00:39:53,000 --> 00:39:54,960
Susan's. Help me give it back to her.

634
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:56,380
[Su Qian]
She didn't know Fei Ke brought someone

635
00:39:56,380 --> 00:39:57,200
to the company.

636
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,200
A visit from a man like Mr. Chen.

637
00:39:59,920 --> 00:40:01,120
Who would ask?

638
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:04,480
When was the last time you saw him?

639
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,080
After I came back from my business trip,

640
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:10,400
I suddenly couldn't reach him.

641
00:40:13,940 --> 00:40:15,660
[Honey, I'm taking off.]

642
00:40:15,660 --> 00:40:16,940
[I landed.]

643
00:40:24,220 --> 00:40:25,380
[Fei Ke]

644
00:40:25,380 --> 00:40:28,840
Sorry, the number you dialed
is out of service.

645
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:29,680
I'm sorry.

646
00:40:36,600 --> 00:40:38,920
Honey, you're also on a business trip?

647
00:40:38,960 --> 00:40:40,200
Are you on a plane?

648
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:42,120
If you land,

649
00:40:42,160 --> 00:40:44,120
message me to let me know
you're alright, okay?

650
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:49,480
Sorry, the number you dialed
is out of service.

651
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:54,720
Sorry, the number you dialed
is out of service.

652
00:40:54,880 --> 00:40:55,640
I'm sorry.

653
00:41:04,360 --> 00:41:05,600
Did you go to look for him?

654
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:09,440
I did.

655
00:41:11,880 --> 00:41:12,800
Whenever he took me to his home,

656
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,440
we always entered from the basement.

657
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:17,040
I couldn't remember
which unit or building it was.

658
00:41:17,400 --> 00:41:18,880
I just remember it was
on the seventh floor.

659
00:41:19,040 --> 00:41:21,360
It was on the seventh floor. Right.

660
00:41:22,440 --> 00:41:23,760
So I had to use my memory

661
00:41:23,760 --> 00:41:25,200
to look from door to door.

662
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:26,880
But it was all so well-decorated,

663
00:41:26,920 --> 00:41:28,520
I couldn't tell the difference.

664
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:29,760
I remember now.

665
00:41:32,400 --> 00:41:33,360
I've seen you before.

666
00:41:41,640 --> 00:41:42,440
Who are you looking for?

667
00:41:44,120 --> 00:41:45,480
Who...who are you?

668
00:41:45,840 --> 00:41:46,640
I'm the owner.

669
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:47,640
What's wrong?

670
00:41:49,640 --> 00:41:51,320
Well, you've been living here all along?

671
00:41:52,120 --> 00:41:52,920
Yeah.

672
00:41:54,600 --> 00:41:56,960
Have you rented this house out before?

673
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:57,840
No.

674
00:41:58,240 --> 00:42:00,120
I've lived here alone all along.

675
00:42:01,880 --> 00:42:02,880
Who on earth are you looking for?

676
00:42:03,440 --> 00:42:05,120
I'm sorry. Excuse me.

677
00:42:08,440 --> 00:42:10,120
That day, I asked you
who you were looking for.

678
00:42:10,440 --> 00:42:11,440
Why didn't you tell me?

679
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:14,680
I didn't want anyone
to know about my relationship with him.

680
00:42:14,920 --> 00:42:15,920
Why not?

681
00:42:16,760 --> 00:42:17,920
Do you know he's married?

682
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:19,200
I really didn't know.

683
00:42:19,640 --> 00:42:21,640
I was trying very hard to find him.

684
00:42:21,680 --> 00:42:22,640
If that day I asked you

685
00:42:22,720 --> 00:42:23,880
and you said his name,

686
00:42:23,960 --> 00:42:25,480
then maybe we'd be on the same page.

687
00:42:25,600 --> 00:42:27,080
Then we could have caught him together.

688
00:42:31,080 --> 00:42:32,200
Did you see him again?

689
00:42:34,960 --> 00:42:35,640
Yes.

690
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,440
What did he lie to you about again?

691
00:43:03,520 --> 00:43:04,360
No way.

692
00:43:05,760 --> 00:43:06,880
What's wrong with you?

693
00:43:06,880 --> 00:43:07,680
I'm fine.

694
00:43:08,120 --> 00:43:08,920
What's going on?

695
00:43:09,000 --> 00:43:10,400
You shouldn't have disappeared.

696
00:43:11,920 --> 00:43:12,960
What's going on?

697
00:43:15,840 --> 00:43:16,640
Something happened to me.

698
00:43:17,720 --> 00:43:18,920
What happened?

699
00:43:25,080 --> 00:43:26,720
Say something.

700
00:43:33,640 --> 00:43:34,160
Well.

701
00:43:35,600 --> 00:43:36,360
You won't say anything?

702
00:43:37,720 --> 00:43:38,960
Then never say it.

703
00:43:39,520 --> 00:43:40,720
And don't contact me again.

704
00:43:49,920 --> 00:43:53,280
What's going on? Tell me.

705
00:43:57,360 --> 00:43:58,440
I didn't contact you

706
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:00,680
because I feared I'd get you into trouble.

707
00:44:03,440 --> 00:44:04,080
What do you mean?

708
00:44:04,120 --> 00:44:05,560
What kind of trouble?

709
00:44:12,120 --> 00:44:14,040
The Series A investor of my project,

710
00:44:15,400 --> 00:44:16,720
we had a good deal.

711
00:44:16,840 --> 00:44:17,880
We've signed the agreement.

712
00:44:19,120 --> 00:44:19,920
I started the project

713
00:44:20,440 --> 00:44:21,840
with my own money.

714
00:44:22,640 --> 00:44:23,920
But he reneged on the deal

715
00:44:24,400 --> 00:44:25,680
and refused to pay.

716
00:44:27,720 --> 00:44:28,440
I don't get it.

717
00:44:30,560 --> 00:44:32,400
Where did you get the money?

718
00:44:33,480 --> 00:44:35,160
I wanted to hold on
until they paid the money,

719
00:44:36,120 --> 00:44:38,640
so I mortgaged all the company's assets

720
00:44:40,800 --> 00:44:42,440
and took out a bridge loan.

721
00:44:43,560 --> 00:44:44,960
But they disappeared completely.

722
00:44:46,600 --> 00:44:48,160
Uh, no, what do you mean?

723
00:44:48,160 --> 00:44:49,160
I don't understand.

724
00:44:51,120 --> 00:44:51,880
Su Qian,

725
00:44:52,560 --> 00:44:53,560
I'm broke.

726
00:44:55,120 --> 00:44:56,600
I'm out of money.

727
00:45:01,120 --> 00:45:01,940
Such a big deal.

728
00:45:01,940 --> 00:45:04,240
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

729
00:45:07,680 --> 00:45:09,400
I'm here today to tell you I'm okay.

730
00:45:10,960 --> 00:45:11,600
Trust me,

731
00:45:11,680 --> 00:45:12,680
I can handle it.

732
00:45:14,240 --> 00:45:15,480
How much do you need?

733
00:45:15,920 --> 00:45:16,920
Never mind.

734
00:45:17,000 --> 00:45:18,120
It's none of your business.

735
00:45:18,120 --> 00:45:20,920
Say something. How much do you need?

736
00:45:23,280 --> 00:45:24,280
Maybe millions.

737
00:45:25,360 --> 00:45:26,440
It has nothing to do with you.

738
00:45:28,000 --> 00:45:28,720
Su Qian,

739
00:45:29,600 --> 00:45:30,880
I may have caused you
a lot of grief lately.

740
00:45:31,640 --> 00:45:32,600
I can't meet you anymore.

741
00:45:33,400 --> 00:45:34,400
Take care of yourself.

742
00:45:39,080 --> 00:45:39,880
Fei Ke.

743
00:45:41,900 --> 00:45:43,600
I'm just here to reassure you today.

744
00:45:44,800 --> 00:45:46,160
I don't want to get you into this.

745
00:46:05,060 --> 00:46:05,820
[Certificate of Property Rights]

746
00:46:26,580 --> 00:46:28,700
[Your account has received
a deposit of 3,000,000 yuan.]

747
00:46:39,340 --> 00:46:40,820
[Su Qian]

748
00:46:41,280 --> 00:46:43,520
I told you this has nothing
to do with you.

749
00:46:44,040 --> 00:46:44,820
Give me your account number.

750
00:46:44,840 --> 00:46:45,880
I'll give it back to you.

751
00:46:46,200 --> 00:46:46,960
Don't worry about it.

752
00:46:47,080 --> 00:46:47,920
Take the money now

753
00:46:47,920 --> 00:46:48,680
and get it fixed.

754
00:46:48,720 --> 00:46:50,280
We'll get through this together, okay?

755
00:46:52,920 --> 00:46:54,600
Where did you get that kind of money?

756
00:47:01,200 --> 00:47:02,000
Fei Ke,

757
00:47:03,560 --> 00:47:04,520
this is the first trouble
that's happened to us

758
00:47:04,560 --> 00:47:05,960
since we've been together.

759
00:47:08,080 --> 00:47:09,160
I want to be there for you.

760
00:47:11,280 --> 00:47:12,840
I want to help you get through this.

761
00:47:14,440 --> 00:47:15,280
Understand?

762
00:47:20,480 --> 00:47:21,160
Okay.

763
00:47:23,520 --> 00:47:24,920
I'll pay you back in a week.

764
00:47:25,680 --> 00:47:26,880
No rush about the money,

765
00:47:28,880 --> 00:47:29,920
but promise me

766
00:47:31,200 --> 00:47:32,480
you'll keep in touch with me,
don't disappear again,

767
00:47:32,640 --> 00:47:33,880
and don't let me worry about you, okay?

768
00:47:39,040 --> 00:47:39,800
I know.

769
00:47:41,520 --> 00:47:42,280
I understand.

770
00:47:52,040 --> 00:47:53,240
Now that I think about it,

771
00:47:54,640 --> 00:47:56,120
it's not so much that he lied to me

772
00:47:57,640 --> 00:47:59,400
but I threw myself into the trap.

773
00:48:00,560 --> 00:48:02,640
Where are you? I want to see you.

774
00:48:11,180 --> 00:48:12,900
Not now, it's too dangerous.

775
00:48:13,220 --> 00:48:14,100
Wait a few days.

776
00:48:14,320 --> 00:48:15,320
I'll send you a location.

