♪Not saying anything,
but feeling uneasy inside♪

779
00:50:12,680 --> 00:50:15,880
♪Still pretending to be happy♪

780
00:50:17,000 --> 00:50:22,640
♪I can't even blame you
for being so cruel♪

781
00:50:23,200 --> 00:50:26,840
♪When you're lost and sad♪

782
00:50:27,720 --> 00:50:31,640
♪I even don't have the right
to comfort you♪

783
00:50:32,080 --> 00:50:37,160
♪I took a script
that has too many twists and turns♪

784
00:50:38,080 --> 00:50:42,560
♪I can't either love or quit,
